{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mes Loisirs</title>
    <style>
    
        body {
            font-family: <link rel="stylesheet" href=Arial black 
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1em;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1 class="texte">Bienvenue sur Ma Page de Loisirs</h1>
</header>

<section>
    <div>
        <h2>Sport</h2>
        <p >I am passionate about <strong>swimming</strong>. I like to swim with friends on trursdays and follow the big tournament on tv .</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2>pastry</h2>
        <p>Apart from sports, I also enjoy <strong>pastry</strong>.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2>Travel</h2>
        <p>Exploring a new place is one of my favorite hobbies. I had the chance to visit several cities and discover different cultures .</p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2024 MonSiteWeb.com | Tous droits réservés.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>

{% endblock %}
